    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223830/extras/ae8346fbc66067ad3936c3c2b2f4e58a.webp?t=1731377700\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of Everlyn Sterling, a new grad undertaking a temp job in a small town<strong> in dead winter</strong>. Little does she know this seemingly ordinary task will soon unveil a mysterious tale of a disturbed spirit. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223830/extras/73058bfaef34effd8c6c818af973f202.poster.avif?t=1731377700\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223830/extras/73058bfaef34effd8c6c818af973f202.webm?t=1731377700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223830/extras/73058bfaef34effd8c6c818af973f202.mp4?t=1731377700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve a series of brain teasers, booby traps, and ciphers set by the ghost. Can you unravel why a once beautiful mansion now harbors a dark, ugly secret? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223830/extras/90de7e5d97b02b40781427b4f02dd812.poster.avif?t=1731377700\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223830/extras/90de7e5d97b02b40781427b4f02dd812.webm?t=1731377700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223830/extras/90de7e5d97b02b40781427b4f02dd812.mp4?t=1731377700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>FEATURES </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Simple point-and-click interface</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Crack escape-room style puzzles </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Explore a quiet haunted world with a minimalist art style </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Make choices that impact your story progression and ending</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Experience a scary and suspenseful story without gore or violence </p></li></ul>",
